products.title: Choices Quintessence Linen Roller Blind
products.description: Practical and stylish, this quintessence linen roller blind will bring a timeless finish to your window. Rich in texture and light in colour, this blind will be the perfect companion for a more neutral dcor, blending in beautifully and adding just a touch of detailing to your practical and stylish, this quintessence linen roller blind will bring a timeless finish to your window.
